score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"我用nikon 嘅,今日就𨍭會去canon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解?nikon video af 真係差到呢.. Nikon 相方面就靚仔啲嘅我覺得 而家canon 啲sensor  叫做進步咗 夠做嘅"},{"pid":"07564b64fae07fb89fc190e07a68c816eac0f121","tid":161802,"uid":35241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係用開左，又成手鏡，轉會成本都唔細，目前我仲係50/50，有冇人可以俾下意見我</blockquote><br />\n我冇成手鏡 得2470.8 70200.8 50.4 放埋佢 同你講 想就去做 遲啲舊野再跌 成本更高 我就係猶豫咗成2年多冇行動 又冇幾千"},{"pid":"16a5f6c9f1e99bb60e39024946cb8f795f2f7379","tid":161802,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用nikon 嘅,今日就𨍭會去canon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解?nikon video af 真係差到呢.. Nikon 相方面就靚仔啲嘅我覺得 而家canon 啲sensor  叫做進步咗 夠做嘅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有咁既事，巴打可唔可以分享多啲轉canon 原因"},{"pid":"4403499f60d734bb7359274f4247eb0ba70e1700","tid":161802,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"nikon鏡接sony body,屋企仲有部D700同FM2<br />\n<br />\n個mount由大F到今日都可以插上去係nikon的一大優勢"},{"pid":"22735cbe0db23348609e1736d8df5f396f846fd1","tid":161802,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申 canon 人，身邊朋友都以canon 為多，但係我想轉會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解轉呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: canon<br />\n<br />\n當年見親NIKON人都成日講到點好點好, 個個大師, CANON走蕉, NIKON鏡又支支強勁 (而且全部靚野), 我又唔想學佢地咁(而且我見到的普遍係老野比較多).<br />\n<br />\n同朋友研究左好似都成半年, 結果揀canon. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f932cae867a214ddba6ee3f1559776053498fa0","tid":161802,"uid":68346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"Canon 個巿場策略做得好，引左你入門就自然沉落去。<br />\n<br />\n入門機外型靚仔， 廣告多，引你落船<br />\n然後開個毒氣室任你試同玩，一中左毒就身痕買鏡<br />\n買多兩買鏡就身痕換body<br />\n一換埋高階body, 習慣左執相個流程，機既操控就唔會再想轉會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Canon 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548504aa17775011ecf48986bf8fa88a4809e1f6","tid":161802,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Canon 個巿場策略做得好，引左你入門就自然沉落去。<br />\n<br />\n入門機外型靚仔， 廣告多，引你落船<br />\n然後開個毒氣室任你試同玩，一中左毒就身痕買鏡<br />\n買多兩買鏡就身痕換body<br />\n一換埋高階body, 習慣左執相個流程，機既操控就唔會再想轉會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Canon 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExect7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2c580078625b7e7b9273a98320dfcd4a97e20b","tid":161802,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"Low Pass Filter"},{"pid":"4f367af26b882806327cd08e75fd8f4fcc305004","tid":161802,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T05:17:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔用Leica?"},{"pid":"b4d3695d52338a5c1da771505986d281ea9aa54e","tid":161802,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Canon 個巿場策略做得好，引左你入門就自然沉落去。<br />\n<br />\n入門機外型靚仔， 廣告多，引你落船<br />\n然後開個毒氣室任你試同玩，一中左毒就身痕買鏡<br />\n買多兩買鏡就身痕換body<br />\n一換埋高階body, 習慣左執相個流程，機既操控就唔會再想轉會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Canon 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExect7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止marketing, 售後服務都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就用慣左成手鏡無謂轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c18a70e672e2cb429a645e09a958194c4171bf","tid":161802,"uid":69792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:07:06.00