ji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止marketing, 售後服務都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就用慣左成手鏡無謂轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哩樣真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日想聽到0的人講canon好說話 <br />\n個心會安樂0的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感覺canon果班人比較謙<br />\nnikon果班就比較認叻同埋老餅（果陣）<br />\nsony就有些似nikon但是比較爛口同埋成日埋怨囉<br />\n<br />\n過宜家我識好多都玩多過一個system<br />\n都冇乜分啦應該就（好似係）<br />\n<br />\n利：canon, polaroid, agfa(film)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger<br />\n好多nikon人都係咁"},{"pid":"322860054d85ce7d571503884030b4100a80c8f3","tid":161802,"uid":65433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"我當年揀的時候原因好簡單<br />\nnikon 快門聲好聽啲"},{"pid":"555163ca540b7463d2773ef63d3b118fc5dc4530","tid":161802,"uid":90246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"紅圈嘅魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCanon 毒氣室堅毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8369ef1b3a3e03b287f42b09aab25e4d17d68f50","tid":161802,"uid":68446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"老豆N年前有多餘錢屎忽痕買左部Nikon FM2 + 一堆AI-S鏡不過唔識用收埋左<br />\n事隔三十年俾我執舊野搵番上水，之後買左部D90慢慢自學+慢慢入AF鏡<br />\n之後工作上(音樂)接觸event/concert影相同拍片，慢慢開始半專業形式入坑"},{"pid":"5a8bc20acb2b33f09064cf3c001de05abf89ff67","tid":161802,"uid":17190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:06:37.000Z","msg":"未正式開始愛上攝影時，追緊的女仔是用c記，不過之後比人溝左，自此就唔用c記的任何產品。<br />\n<br />\n利申：n記人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff21d93ed7441838c72d336c9363e20b5f07184","tid":161802,"uid":19568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T13:06:42.000Z","msg":"朋友介紹之下，入左部D90<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4914cb802d845595d46e5c6358bebd69bbc47db","tid":161802,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未正式開始愛上攝影時，追緊的女仔是用c記，不過之後比人溝左，自此就唔用c記的任何產品。<br />\n<br />\n利申：n記人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dec43652761d5a0441ba86af967622516ec578","tid":161802,"uid":92766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"Canon 80d <br />\n最近想轉去Nikon 因為ff 平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfb7ca9753ec2dd6a4e5d736cd108273bf4e2d5","tid":161802,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"因為nikon後製空間大<br />\nd 相無咁易死黑死白 萬一失手後期都救得翻<br />\n同埋後期暗位拉返光無咁易會出現d 怪色粒粒<br />\n仲有灰階密d<br />\n我覺得影商品同人像時明暗過渡比較自然比較立體<br />\n仲有當初買相機時覺得nikon機既前後轉輪岩我手型d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ea81f14e1c438304cac41b67f2284e70c28403","tid":161802,"uid":35241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我用nikon 嘅,今日就𨍭會去canon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  點解?nikon video af 真係差到呢.. Nikon 相方面就靚仔啲嘅我覺得 而家canon 啲sensor  叫做進步咗 夠做嘅</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有咁既事，巴打可唔可以分享多啲轉canon 原因</blockquote><br />\n今日去咗買機喇,聽日買埋鏡.本身就係咪都upgrade 嘅,見D5