sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExect7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到，dpp 好好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 我反而想入部罪大a7ii 插50L, 有時真係舞佢唔掂，但又鍾意50L出黎d相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經幾年無開dpp, 淨用lightroom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢家習慣左影raw 加jpg, 影完wifi jpg 上iphone 再back 上icloud, raw 就定期up 上電腦，執完又食埋入icloud, 變左三個backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nCanon 既紅圈又係一個好緊要既trademark, 唔識相機，但見到個紅圈都會free 到係貴野，吸引到好多要型既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb4c618e3025f00017ddc7e261e7fbe88862ac6","tid":161802,"uid":4712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Canon 個巿場策略做得好，引左你入門就自然沉落去。<br />\n<br />\n入門機外型靚仔， 廣告多，引你落船<br />\n然後開個毒氣室任你試同玩，一中左毒就身痕買鏡<br />\n買多兩買鏡就身痕換body<br />\n一換埋高階body, 習慣左執相個流程，機既操控就唔會再想轉會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：Canon 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nExect7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n駁唔到，dpp 好好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 我反而想入部罪大a7ii 插50L, 有時真係舞佢唔掂，但又鍾意50L出黎d相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經幾年無開dpp, 淨用lightroom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢家習慣左影raw 加jpg, 影完wifi jpg 上iphone 再back 上icloud, raw 就定期up 上電腦，執完又食埋入icloud, 變左三個backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nCanon 既紅圈又係一個好緊要既trademark, 唔識相機，但見到個紅圈都會free 到係貴野，吸引到好多要型既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實質好多紅圈都平過其他廠既鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/2